Description:
  The source code for Clutter, a middleware drawing and animation library used
by the window manager.

Local Modification:
- Fixed autoconf to work with GLES libraries with non-standard names
- Fixed autoconf to not link both GLES and GL at the same time
- Fixed a NULL pointer reference in x11_set_stage_foreign
- Implement cogl_get_proc_address and cogl_check_extension for Cogl GLES
- Added ClutterEGLXEGLImage.
- Addded a sample for masking.

